  <div id="app_wrap" class="ema523_02_su_0003">
    <section class="title type2">
      <h2 data-head="1_pink" lang="y">모양과 크기가 같은 도형을 만들어 봅시다.</h2>
    </section>

    <section class="contents paging_layout">
      <div class="flex align_start gap_26">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">색종이 한 장에 도형을 그리고, 그 아래에 다른 색종이 한 장을 겹쳐서 오려 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box mt_20 justify_center">
            <div class="dragndrop_fraction_wrap drow_wrap">
              <canvas id="pathCanvas"></canvas>
              <div class="icon_hand"><img src="../../common_contents/common/img/cursor_pointer_small.svg" alt="손모양 이미지"></div>
              <div class="drag_group">
                  <div class="drag_item dragpable" data-pair="1">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="280" height="239" viewBox="0 0 280 239" fill="none">
                      <path d="M2.17725 68.4618H159.273V2.82764L277.453 120.267L159.273 236.856V172.338H2.17725V68.4618Z" stroke="#1D1D1B" stroke-width="3.97745" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="drag_item dragpable scissors" data-pair="2">
                    <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_02_SU/img_scissors.svg" alt="가위 이미지">
                  </div>
              </div>
              <div class="icon_arrow">
                <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_02_SU/icon_arrow.svg" alt="화살표 이미지">
              </div>
              <div class="drop_group">
                  <div class="drop_item droppable" data-pair="1" data-answer-single="empty_answer"></div>
                  <div class="drop_item droppable scissors" data-pair="2"></div>
                  <div class="img_motion"><img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_02_SU/img_motion.gif" alt="종이 오리기 모션 이미지"></div>
              </div>
              <div class="spread-piece_group">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="280" height="239" viewBox="0 0 280 239" fill="#EF7D00" class="spread-piece1">
                  <path d="M2.17725 68.4618H159.273V2.82764L277.453 120.267L159.273 236.856V172.338H2.17725V68.4618Z" stroke="#1D1D1B" stroke-width="3.97745" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
                <div class="icon_arrow">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA523_02_SU/icon_arrow.svg" alt="화살표 이미지">
                </div>
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="280" height="239" viewBox="0 0 280 239" fill="#6368AE" class="spread-piece2">
                  <path d="M2.17725 68.4618H159.273V2.82764L277.453 120.267L159.273 236.856V172.338H2.17725V68.4618Z" stroke="#1D1D1B" stroke-width="3.97745" stroke-linejoin="round"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      <article class="page page_2">
